OL,6,FMr Staunton, who took up the role in
OL,7,FDecember 2022 following nine years as
OL,8,Fchairman of WH Smith, suggested that
OL,9,Fthe alleged request was linked to
OL,10,Fconcerns about the cost of
OL,11,Fcompensation heading into the election.
OL,13,FHe told the Sunday Times newspaper:
OL,14,F"Early on, I was told by a fairly
OL,15,Fsenior person to stall on spend on
OL,16,Fcompensation and on the replacement of
OL,17,FHorizon, and to limp, in quotation
OL,18,Fmarks ` I did a file note on it ` limp
OL,19,Finto the election.
