OL,6,F"It was not an anti-postmaster thing,
OL,7,Fit was just straight financials. I
OL,8,Fdidn't ask, because I said 'I'm having
OL,9,Fno part of it ` I'm not here to limp
OL,10,Finto the election, it's not the right
OL,11,Fthing to do by postmasters'.
OL,13,F"The word 'limp' gives you a snapshot
OL,14,Fof where they were."
OL,16,FThe scandal has been pushed into the
OL,17,Fpublic eye by a major ITV drama into
OL,18,Fthe long legal fight by subpostmasters
OL,19,Fto get justice.
